  <brief_title>Prospective Evaluation of Femoral Versus Femoral and Sciatic Nerve Block for Ambulatory Anterior Cruciate Ligament (ACL) Reconstruction</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Addition of a Preoperative Sciatic Nerve Block to a Femoral Nerve Block for Ambulatory Arthroscopic ACL Reconstruction</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>University of California, San Francisco</agency>
